<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>td — simple task tracker</title>
    <meta name="description" content="SQLite task tracker. Single bash script. Works offline." />
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      
      :root {
        --bg: #fff;
        --fg: #111;
        --muted: #666;
        --border: #e5e5e5;
        --code-bg: #f5f5f5;
        --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        --mono: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
      }
      
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --bg: #111;
          --fg: #eee;
          --muted: #888;
          --border: #333;
          --code-bg: #1a1a1a;
        }
      }
      
      html {
        font-family: var(--font);
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--fg);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      
      body {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      
      p {
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .install {
        background: var(--code-bg);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }
      
      h2 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      li {
        padding: 0.25rem 0;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      
      li code {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--fg);
      }
      
      footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
      
      a {
        color: var(--fg);
      }
      
      @media (max-width: 480px) {
        body { padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
        .install { font-size: 0.75rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>td</h1>
    
    <p>A task tracker for AI coding agents. I liked <a href="https://github.com/beads-org/beads">beads</a>, but somewhere along the way it became more than I wanted. So I made this.</p>
    
    <p>One bash script. SQLite. No dependencies. Agents can read and write tasks without any setup.</p>
    
    <div class="install">curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alosec/td-world/main/install.sh | bash</div>
    
    <h2>Commands</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>td create "fix bug" -p 1</code> — create task</li>
      <li><code>td list</code> — show tasks</li>
      <li><code>td move abc-123 todo</code> — change status</li>
      <li><code>td close abc-123</code> — mark done</li>
      <li><code>td dep add abc-123 xyz-456</code> — add blocker</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>There's also <code>tv</code>, an fzf viewer with table and kanban modes.</p>
    
    <footer>
      <a href="https://github.com/alosec/td-world">GitHub</a>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
